lfsr-generator NEWS -- history of user-visible changes.

New in 1.0.2:
* shift-left support.
* C++ support.
* Function template support.
* Namespace support.
* Function qualifier support.
* New options: `--include-guard', `--includes', `--no-extern-c-guard',
  `--prototype' and `--no-auto'.

New in 1.0.1:
* New option `--header'.  `--target=...' is obsoleted.

New in 1.0.0:
* Initial release.
